				<div class="talk-intro">
					<p id="tagline" class="notranslate">Eric Topol says we'll soon use our smartphones to monitor our vital signs and chronic conditions. At TEDMED, he highlights several of the most important wireless devices in medicine's future -- all helping to keep more of us out of hospital beds.</p>
											<p>
							Eric Topol is a leading cardiologist who has embraced the study of genomics and the latest advances in technology to treat chronic disease.  <a target="_blank" title="Eric Topol's bio" href="/speakers/eric_topol.html">Full bio »</a>						</p>
					
